S1 E13

TV-14 D, V, L 42min | 2020

Tuesdays 10/9c

When a case of cyber-stalking escalates to multiple murders, the team must track down a hacker who will stop at nothing to get revenge on those he believes have wronged him. Also, someone from Hana's past offers her help on the case, but at a price she's not willing to pay. (TV-14 D, L, V) Air Date: Apr 28, 2020
